data.description: Beautiful ranch-style home on over 8ac provides plenty of opportunities to enjoy nature & the great outdoors. Property boasts a 3-bed, 1-bath home welcoming you in w/ a cozy wood-burning stove in the living room, eat-in kitchen has ss appliances & sliding glass doors that lead to the patio & yard large enough for all your gardening, recreational, or nature observing pursuits. The finished basement provides additional living space & storage. Property also features central air to keep cool during hot summer months, seller owned solar panels to help save on energy costs & an oversized 2 car attached garage providing ample space for vehicles, storage, or even a workshop. About 30 mins west of Albany & just over 1 mile to Thacher Park! Don't miss this incredible opportunity!
